## 3. API Structure (Next.js Route Handlers)

### Fee Structure
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/admin/finance/fee-structures` | List all fee structures |
| POST | `/api/admin/finance/fee-structures` | Create fee structure |
| PUT | `/api/admin/finance/fee-structures/[id]` | Update fee structure |
| DELETE | `/api/admin/finance/fee-structures/[id]` | Delete (if no payments linked) |

### Fee Payments
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/admin/finance/payments` | List all payments (filterable by session, status) |
| GET | `/api/admin/finance/payments/[studentId]` | Student's full payment history |
| POST | `/api/admin/finance/payments/[studentId]` | Add a payment entry |
| GET | `/api/student/finance/payments` | Student views own payments |

### Expenses
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/admin/finance/expenses` | List expenses (filterable by month/category) |
| POST | `/api/admin/finance/expenses` | Add expense |
| PUT | `/api/admin/finance/expenses/[id]` | Edit expense |
| DELETE | `/api/admin/finance/expenses/[id]` | Delete expense |

### Salary
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/admin/finance/salary` | List salary records (filterable by month) |
| POST | `/api/admin/finance/salary` | Create monthly salary records |
| PUT | `/api/admin/finance/salary/[id]` | Mark as paid / update |

### Dashboard
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/admin/finance/dashboard` | Returns all summary stats |

